cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.MM

This paper deals with visual recognition systems and their operational challenges, which are typically addressed in the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) communities. The paper also presents a new algorithm for open world recognition, which falls under the broader umbrella of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the issue of outlier detection, which is a common problem in computer security (cs.CR). Finally, the experiments are conducted on a large-scale image dataset, which is relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) research.
